{"id": "dey1665702662999", "title": "findkey", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "findkey"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dey1665702662999.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">findkey</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: finally  \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: finally  \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nab1665702580017.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: flush \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: flush \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qmr1720023923858.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/dey1665702662999.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/dey1665702662999.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/dey1665702662999.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526775\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526775\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 19, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dey1665702662999.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dey1665702662999.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dey1665702662999.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dey1665702662999\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"dey1665702662999__findkey_221836\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Check if the key value of an entity exists.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dey1665702662999__topic_d72848e1_d72849e1_d72850e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dey1665702662999__p_d72851e1_d72852e1_d72853e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">findkey</span> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"dey1665702662999__section_w430ab1b7b5_w431ab1b7_w432ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dey1665702662999__p_d72854e1_d72855e1_d72856e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">findkey $entname, 1</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dey1665702662999__topic_d47922e1_d47923e1_d47924e1_d47925e1_d47926e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d457529e82\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6626e1_d6627e1_d6628e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6626e1_d6627e1_d6628e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6626e1_d6627e1_d6628e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6626e1_d6627e1_d6628e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6626e1_d6627e1_d6628e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6626e1_d6627e1_d6628e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6626e1_d6627e1_d6628e1__entry__3\">\n Name of the Entity where the key is to be located.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6626e1_d6627e1_d6628e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6626e1_d6627e1_d6628e1__entry__2\">\n Number\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6626e1_d6627e1_d6628e1__entry__3\">\n Value that identifies the key to be located; whole (integer) number; the value will be truncated to form an integer.\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dey1665702662999__li_d32318e1_d32319e1_d32320e1\">1, the primary key.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dey1665702662999__li_d32321e1_d32322e1_d32323e1\">2, 3, 4, and so on, the number that identifies a candidate key; indexes are not allowed.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dey1665702662999__topic_d47927e1_d47928e1_d47929e1_d47930e1_d47931e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d457529e160\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1__entry__2\">\n Primary or candidate key, <var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>, of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> does not exist.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1__entry__2\"> Primary or candidate key,\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>, of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> already exists\n                        in the component. <code class=\"ph codeph\">$result</code> contains the occurrence number. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6629e1_d6630e1_d6631e1__entry__2\">\n Primary or candidate key, <var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>, of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> already exists in the database.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">findkey</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Error constant</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-12</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UIOSERR_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Errors during database I/O.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-30</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UNETERR_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Errors during network I/O.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1128</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_NOT_A_KEY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">The key number specified is an index.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1104</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_KEY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dey1665702662999__table_d6632e1_d6633e1_d6634e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">The key number provided is not valid; for example, the key number was out of range.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dey1665702662999__topic_d47932e1_d47933e1_d47934e1_d47935e1_d47936e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d457529e434\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dey1665702662999__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dey1665702662999__topic_d47937e1_d47938e1_d47939e1_d47940e1_d47941e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d457529e443\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dey1665702662999__p_d72872e1_d72873e1_d72874e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">findkey</span> statement checks whether the values of the fields that make up the specified <var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var> in <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> exist, either in the component or in the database. No validation is performed; only a check for the existence of the key.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dey1665702662999__p_d72875e1_d72876e1_d72877e1\">Unlike the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/o</span> statement, which provides additional functionality such as repositioning and recovering removed occurrences, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">findkey</span> only checks for the existence of a key.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dey1665702662999__p_d72878e1_d72879e1_d72880e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">findkey</span> statement is especially useful in the validateKey trigger, while <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/o</span> should be used in the leaveModifiedKey trigger. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">findkey</span> statement checks for existence of a specified key, referred to by its key number, while <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/o</span> looks for the ‘first’ complete key, using the order in which the keys are defined. This means that <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/o</span> only works for candidate keys if the primary key data is not available.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dey1665702662999__p_d72881e1_d72882e1_d72883e1\">If the arguments are omitted, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">findkey</span> looks for the primary key of the current entity. This is equivalent to the following statement:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">findkey $entname, 1</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">findkey</span> statement:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">findkey $entname, $NEWKEYVALUE$</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sse1719818928383.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$curkey</a><p>Return the number of the current key in a validateKey or leaveModifiedKey trigger.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/upd1665702601935.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keytype</a><p>Return the type of the specified key.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/epv1719810593542.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$totkeys</a><p>Return the total number of keys for an entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kld1665702599590.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>retrieve/o</a><p>Attempt to locate an occurrence of an entity using the current primary key value.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1665702576817.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatekey</a><p>Validate a key of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/frh1665703129863.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger validateKey</a><p>System trigger that defines the procedural checks to validate a modified primary or candidate key.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526775\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526775\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "findkey Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 19, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Check if the key value of an entity exists. findkey { Entity , KeyNumber } Example: findkey $entname, 1 Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Name of the Entity where the key is to be located. KeyNumber Number Value that identifies the key to be located; whole (integer) number; the value will be truncated to form an integer. 1, the primary key. 2, 3, 4, and so on, the number that identifies a candidate key; indexes are not allowed. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $status Value Description -1 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. 0 Primary or candidate key, KeyNumber , of Entity does not exist. 1 Primary or candidate key, KeyNumber , of Entity already exists in the component. $result contains the occurrence number. 2 Primary or candidate key, KeyNumber , of Entity already exists in the database. Table 3. Values commonly returned by $procerror following findkey Value Error constant Meaning -2 through -12 <UIOSERR_*> Errors during database I/O. -16 through -30 <UNETERR_*> Errors during network I/O. -1128 <UPROCERR_NOT_A_KEY> The key number specified is an index. -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. -1104 <UPROCERR_KEY> The key number provided is not valid; for example, the key number was out of range. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The findkey statement checks whether the values of the fields that make up the specified KeyNumber in Entity exist, either in the component or in the database. No validation is performed; only a check for the existence of the key. Unlike the retrieve/o statement, which provides additional functionality such as repositioning and recovering removed occurrences, findkey only checks for the existence of a key. The findkey statement is especially useful in the validateKey trigger, while retrieve/o should be used in the leaveModifiedKey trigger. The findkey statement checks for existence of a specified key, referred to by its key number, while retrieve/o looks for the ‘first’ complete key, using the order in which the keys are defined. This means that retrieve/o only works for candidate keys if the primary key data is not available. If the arguments are omitted, findkey looks for the primary key of the current entity. This is equivalent to the following statement: findkey $entname, 1 Copy The following example uses the findkey statement: findkey $entname, $NEWKEYVALUE$ Copy Related Links $curkey Return the number of the current key in a validateKey or leaveModifiedKey trigger. $keytype Return the type of the specified key. $totkeys Return the total number of keys for an entity. retrieve/o Attempt to locate an occurrence of an entity using the current primary key value. validatekey Validate a key of the current occurrence. trigger validateKey System trigger that defines the procedural checks to validate a modified primary or candidate key. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}